description:
In this karaoke video, I'll be performing "Peace in the Valley". If you're looking for a fun and easy way to add some fun to your karaoke night, then this is the song for you!
Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned karaoke enthusiast, this is the song for you! I'll be performing the vocals live, so you can enjoy the full experience! 

Music performed and mixed by C Lalhmuaka
3 Sisters Youtube Production
Motion Graphics Used : SIMPLE CREATIONS by Joe Hackney
https://www.youtube.com/c/GospelProductionsbyJoeHackney
